data.title: Caganers Celebrities
data.meta_description: In this section we intend to offer a range of Caganers that can be placed easily in the world of celebrities. That is the reason why we have added several sections, among which you can find actors, singers, football players and other sportmen, politicians, members of the Royal Family and immortal figures. Since they have done a good job, we pay tribute to their career with a Caganer in order to bring them luck. In 2002 we elaborated the first Caganers —Jordi Pujol, Pasqual Maragall and Artur Mas, three Catalan politicians— and it was such a success that we put heart into continue the series. Currently there are a lot of celebrities that feel proud of their Caganer, check them out!
